`= 3|x|^2 + 3|x| + 1`

Therefore, `|y^3 - x^3| = |y - x| * |y^2 + xy + x^2| ≤ |y - x| * (3|x|^2 + 3|x| + 1)`

We want `|y - x| * (3|x|^2 + 3|x| + 1) < ε`. We can choose `δ` such that `|y - x| < δ` implies the above is less than `ε`.

